<h1 class="fullWidth">Current Publications: Law, justice and rights</h1>
<h2 class="legis">Freedom of Religion and Religious Symbols in the Public Sphere <!--<a name="txt0" id="txt0"></a><a class="footnote" href="#note" title="Note">*</a>--></h2>
</div> 
<!--end of topHeading div--> 
