European Court of Human Rights, El Morsli v. France (Application n<sup>o</sup>. 15585/06), 4 March 2008.
<span class="print_off"><span class="nowrap">&#91; <a href="#txt103" title="Return to text note 103">Return to text</a> &#93;</span></span></li>

